00:39:09,180 --> 00:39:11,120
Come on, have some water.

394
00:39:12,700 --> 00:39:17,320
 I misunderstood. I shouldn't have rashly given him the hairpin. 

395
00:39:28,900 --> 00:39:30,700
Miss Xiao is an outsider, after all.

396
00:39:30,700 --> 00:39:35,300
Have the banquet here is one thing, but Master Jiang asked you to organize it too.

397
00:39:35,300 --> 00:39:36,619
How could they?

398
00:39:36,619 --> 00:39:39,860
It's not him, it's Xue Xi.

399
00:39:39,860 --> 00:39:43,820
Xue Xi did it to support our business.

400
00:39:43,820 --> 00:39:46,660
For a single banquet, she gave us 500 strings.

401
00:39:46,660 --> 00:39:51,059
This money is enough to renovate all of Fragrance Garden.

402
00:39:51,059 --> 00:39:54,879
We must put our heart into it and not let down their goodwill.

403
00:40:00,919 --> 00:40:03,640
Da Fu, you can't paste it like this.

404
00:40:03,640 --> 00:40:09,080
You need to paste each piece of flower neatly, so it looks like a carpet.

405
00:40:09,080 --> 00:40:12,700
Look, don't leave too many gaps.

406
00:40:12,700 --> 00:40:16,459
These crape myrtle flowers were expensively shipped from Jiangnan.

407
00:40:16,459 --> 00:40:22,019
They could live a few days more in a vase. It's a pity to cover the ground with them.

408
00:40:22,019 --> 00:40:24,120
Are all nobles this extravagant?

409
00:40:24,120 --> 00:40:25,499
You can't say that.

410
00:40:25,499 --> 00:40:28,560
Since we've taken their money and accepted the order,

411
00:40:28,560 --> 00:40:31,340
we should do it well according to their requirements.

412
00:40:31,340 --> 00:40:34,539
How can we complain about the client just because of our own reluctance?

413
00:40:34,539 --> 00:40:38,439
Sister, take a break. I brought some tea over.

414
00:40:39,419 --> 00:40:41,959
- Come on, let's take a break. 
 - Alright.

415
00:40:44,180 --> 00:40:46,499
Do you want to have some water?

416
00:40:46,499 --> 00:40:49,300
- Thank you, Shopkeeper, it's not necessary. 
 - Thank you for your hard work.

417
00:40:49,300 --> 00:40:50,840
Let's go.

418
00:40:55,860 --> 00:40:57,760
Thank you, Young Master Liu.

419
00:41:01,619 --> 00:41:05,019
I found out from A'Hui, no wonder so many flowers are needed.

420
00:41:05,019 --> 00:41:10,680
This setup is because Miss Xiao wants to confess her feelings to Master Jiang.

421
00:41:14,579 --> 00:41:17,939
She may express it herself, but Master Jiang might not accept it.

422
00:41:19,699 --> 00:41:23,380
Excuse me, is that the dilapidated house beside the garden?

423
00:41:24,539 --> 00:41:27,099
What dilapidated house? That's our residence.

424
00:41:27,099 --> 00:41:28,699
What's the matter?

425
00:41:30,260 --> 00:41:36,800
Are you both from the Imperial Workshop? Is Jiang Residence going to be renovated?

426
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:39,600
Indeed, Miss Xiao likes pavilions and towers.

